# Common config
_common (Provides): { threshold: 99.9, window_in_days: 7 }

## Success Rate SLOs
"sync_job" extends [_common]:
  Guarantees 99.9% over 30d window as measured by "success_rate" with: { job_name: "sync" }

"event_job" extends [_common]:
  Guarantees 99.9% over 30d window as measured by "success_rate" with: { job_name: "event" }

"event_latency" extends [_common]:
  Guarantees 99.9% over 30d window as measured by "latency_10m" with: { job_name: "event" }

"sync_latency" extends [_common]:
  Guarantees 99.9% over 30d window as measured by "latency_1h" with: { job_name: "sync" }
